===Pronunciation===
הוה    הוא / hâvâ'  hâvâh / haw-vaw', haw-vaw'

===Etymology===
A primitive root (compare {{HH|183}}, {{HH|1961}}) supposed to mean properly to breathe;

===Verb===
'''הוא'''

# To [[be]] (in the sense of existence): - be, X have.

